zhejiang export fair opens in hcm city an_international expo named zhejiang made all need was opened at saigon exhibition convention centre secc in ho chi_minh city on august bringing together more than 100 major exporters from zhejiang china booth at the sixth zhejiang export fair in hanoi source vna this fair the eighth edition of its kind features 150 booths displaying zhejiang made products in four main sectors construction_materials and_interiors machines electronics_and electrical products bicycles and_parts and_textile materials_and consumer_goods number_of business matching conferences will be organised on the sidelines of_the expo for different industries for example electrical_appliances and_electric cars and_electrical engineering thes e_events provide an_opportunity for enterprises both at_home and_overseas to learn about export products made on eu standards launched in 2011 the event is one of_the largest exhibition for export commodities hosted by zhejiang in asean member countries which has played significant part in boosting trade relations between_vietnam and_the chinese province vietnam is biggest trade partner in southeast asia last year bilateral trade between_vietnam and_zhejiang reached 9.39 billion usd up 18.4_percent from year earlier vna

closing ceremony of_the 11 th cooperation connection_and enterprise development in the north conference in 2018 after days the 11 th northern regional cooperation connection and_enterprise development forum conference in 2018 with the theme enhancing the role_of business associations in supporting_small and_medium enterprises with sustainable development completed the content of the_proposal and_closed at noon on november 17 2018 at the eleventh forum the whole conference agreed to approve the resolution with some contents related to the focus on exploiting the law on_small and_medium enterprises support focusing on supporting the target program that has been stipulated in the law decrees resolutions_and directives of_the government and_the prime minister continue to connect activities to enhance_cooperation and_dialogue between_businesses and state agencies continue to develop_policies and_laws improve_the business_environment and_enhance participation in the reform of_administrative procedures of_the government association system from the central to local_levels join hands with the_government and_local authorities to encourage businesses in building customs creating_habits and_sense of compliance with the law to say no to_negativity undertable costs must be denied as part of_the game rules continue to support the establishment of_new business_associations and_improvement of_their operational capacity strengthening and_promoting cooperation with_international business representative organizations to help vietnamese smes invest abroad gradually forming a_network to support vietnamese enterprises in another country improving the awareness of_society and_the state about the image of_vietnamese entrepreneurs as they are not only getting weathier but also caring for_society and_the community_and they can_fully become an_effective partner of_the state in realizing the social goals at the same time encouraging_businesses and_entrepreneurs to actively participate in programs to ensure social security poverty reduction and_consequences of natural disasters through the forum the business community sent to the government some recommendations such_as firstly the government should continue to improve_policies investment_and business_environment create favorable conditions for small_and medium enterprises focus on the implementation of_credit finance tax technology production premises promotion_and market expansion public procurement information and_advice developing human resources creating_and providing services to support businesses in joining_and withdrawing from the market secondly the government needs to have solutions to transfer some public services from ministries branches and_localities to business_associations subsequently reducing the cost of_enterprises in production_and_business and_also emphasizing the associations capacity and_responsibility thereby mobilizing resources in society and_contributing partly to reduce costs from the state budget thirdly the government should soon submit to the national assembly for promulgating the law on associations to promote the development_of business associations with the extensive participation of_smes that the associations will have a_solid clear and_strong legal foundation our mission is to contribute to the socio-economic development the development of each_industry and_the development of_each business in the immediate future it is possible to_study develop_and issue separate decree on_organization and operation_of business_associations fourthly the government should continue the administrative reform cut down_on business conditions with particular attention to the areas related to_construction land environment investment tax customs and_defense urging state agencies to promote the application of_information technology to solve administrative procedures in online form and_improving business investment environment in the spirit of_the resolution it is recommended that the government should soon apply electronic communication systems_between business registration_agencies tax_authorities and_social insurance to simplify the establishment of_enterprises fifthly the government should pay attention to creating conditions for vietnam smes_association and_local business associations to participate in working missions of government_leaders and_ministries and_branches in foreign activities as a_result the associations can_exchange study_and work more with international_organizations and_participate more in implementing programs of_the government as well as of_ministries branches_and localities on issues related to enterprise development in general and_smes in particular the leader of_quang_ninh business association handed over the circulating flag to_phu_tho business association to host the 12 th forum some images at the closing ceremony of_the conference representatives at the conference ministries representatives at the conference business associations signed cooperation agreement mr nguyen van than chairman of_vinasme nguyễn_hoàng_lân
